OL,5, Evangelical Christian leader Pat       
OL,6, Robertson, who ran for president as a  
OL,7, Republican, has died at the age of 93. 
OL,9,FHe was one of the driving forces of a  
OL,10,Fmovement to increase the influence of  
OL,11,Fthe religious right in US politics.    
OL,13,FHe founded the Christian Broadcasting  
OL,14,FNetwork (CBN) in 1960 and helped grow  
OL,15,Fit into a cable media empire.          
OL,17,FFor decades, Robertson hosted a CBN    
OL,18,Ftalk show called the 700 Club that     
OL,19,Fcombined religious news and political  
OL,20,Fcommentary with light entertainment.   
